title: Canadian Utilities Appoints Jennifer Westacott to Board of Directors
snippet: 2, 2025 /CNW/ - Canadian Utilities Limited (TSX: CU) Canadian Utilities Limited is pleased to announce the appointment of Jennifer Westacott AO to its Board of Directors, effective immediately.

title: Wesfarmers Announces Director Transition with Julie Coates - TipRanks.com
snippet: Wesfarmers Limited has announced that Jennifer Westacott will retire as a director at the end of her term in 2025, with Julie Coates set to join the board as a non-executive director from May 2025.
